<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>ESG职业人格测试 | 商道学堂 · 发现你的绿色使命</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e9f5e9 0%, #c8e6df 100%);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
